@page "/about"
@attribute [Route("/about-us")]

<div class="container mt-4">

    <h1 class="text-center">About Botwatch.xyz</h1>

    <p class="lead text-center mb-5">
        Botwatch is a passion project that tracks how bots, crawlers, and scrapers interact with websites —
        separating the curious from the malicious, and shining a light on what automated traffic is really doing online.
    </p>

    <div class="row mb-4">
        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
            <div class="glass-card">
                <h3>🔍 What We Do</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Log every request’s IP, headers, user agent, and route</li>
                    <li>Detect headless bots, scrapers, and impersonators</li>
                    <li>Deploy traps like fake admin pages and hidden fields</li>
                    <li>Identify bad bots and known crawlers</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
            <div class="glass-card">
                <h3>💭 Why We Do It</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Over 50% of web traffic is bots — and many are harmful</li>
                    <li>We want to validate these stats with real data</li>
                    <li>Reveal where bots come from and how they behave</li>
                    <li>Expose botnets and stealth scraping attempts</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mb-4">
        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
            <div class="glass-card">
                <h3>📊 What’s Coming</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>A public dashboard to view bot activity in real time</li>
                    <li>A leaderboard of top bots ranked by behavior</li>
                    <li>Breakdowns by country, provider, and crawl type</li>
                    <li>Open data for researchers and curious devs</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
            <div class="glass-card">
                <h3>🤝 Who Built This & How to Contribute</h3>
                <p>
                    Botwatch.xyz was created by <strong>Matthew Williams</strong>. If you'd like to contribute or build your own version, feel free to fork the repo on GitHub:
                </p>
                <p>
                    🔗 <a href="https://github.com/yeahlolnice" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Botwatch.xyz Repo</a>
                </p>
                <p>
                    Got ideas or bot trap suggestions? Visit the <a href="/suggest">Suggest</a> page to share them.
                </p>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 20px;">
                    <p>
                        <a href="https://github.com/yeahlolnice" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">
                            <i class="bi bi-github"></i>
                        </a>
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/matthew-williams-128154197/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">
                            <i class="bi bi-linkedin"></i>
                        </a>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
